  "body": "### Description\r\nSign to Status.\r\nGo to chats.\r\nSelect Contact \r\nclick on /location\r\nSelect Deny\r\nAfter selecting Deny also, app is trying to Send the location & screen is appearing as following screenshot.\r\n![sendloc](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20433356/33834896-a5ed4cc6-deaa-11e7-9deb-098de035b318.png)\r\nNote - Please see Time is also varying with actual  time & app time.\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: ...\r\nAfter selecting Deny, then it shouldn't send the location. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nAfter selecting Deny, then app shouldn't send the location. \r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nIt's sending the location after User deny, then also & running in infinite loop.\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\nShould verify whether User is allowing or denying to send the location.\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: ...\r\nartifacts.status.im:8081/artifactory/nightlies-local/im.status.ethereum-ee2904.apk\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Android 6.0.1\r\n\r\n\r\n",
